<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الوَحْىَ يأْتِيهَا،<span class="c5"> وَكَانَ أَبوهَا يُؤْمِن بهَا وَيَقُول فِي أَيْمَانِه:</span> وحَقِّ بِنْتِي النَّبِيَّةِ قَالَ <span class="c2">(عبد الله بن)</span> مُحَمَّد بن سِنَانٍ الخَفَاجِيّ يُخَاطِبه:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِحَيَاةِ زَيْنَبَ يَا ابْنَ عَبْدِ الوَاحِدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وبِحَقِّ كُلِّ نَبِيَّةٍ فِي <span class="c3">{يَاقِدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مَا صَارَ عَنْدَكَ رَوْشَنُ بنُ مُحَسِّنٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فِيمَا يَقُولُ الناسُ أَعْدَلَ شَاهِدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>كَذَا فِي المعجم لياقُوت.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَمِمَّا يسْتَدرك عَلَيْهِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[يكد]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>:} يَكُودَه: قَرْيَة بإِفرِيقِيَةَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>